         <div type="translation">
            <ab>OIM 19347, recto: (1) Taminis daughter of Parates, 1/12(?) silver (kite) for the (2) price of oil of Payni, has written (3) Esminis (on) Egyptian year 36(?), Epeiph 12(?)</ab>
